#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "HTTP/3 Reference"
msgstr "HTTP/3 参考手册"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "HTTP/3 support is **experimental**. Configuration properties and behavior may change in future releases."
msgstr "HTTP/3 支持目前处于 *实验阶段* 。配置属性及行为在未来的版本中可能会发生变化。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"HTTP/3 is the latest version of the HTTP protocol.\n"
"It replaces TCP with https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9000[QUIC], a transport protocol built on UDP that provides built-in encryption, reduced connection setup latency, and elimination of head-of-line blocking."
msgstr "HTTP/3 是 HTTP 协议的最新版本。它用 link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9000[QUIC] 取代了 TCP， link:https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/rfc9000[QUIC] 是一种基于 UDP 的传输协议，具有内置加密功能，可降低连接建立延迟，并消除了队列头阻塞。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"From an application perspective, HTTP/3 is transparent: request and response handling is identical to HTTP/1.1 and HTTP/2.\n"
"The same handlers, filters, and endpoints work across all three protocols.\n"
"The only differences are at the transport level — QUIC uses UDP instead of TCP, and TLS 1.3 is mandatory."
msgstr "从应用角度来看，HTTP/3 是透明的：请求和响应的处理方式与 HTTP/1.1 和 HTTP/2 完全相同。这三种协议均可使用相同的处理程序、过滤器和端点。唯一的区别在于传输层——QUIC 使用 UDP 而不是 TCP，并且必须使用 TLS 1.3。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus serves HTTP/1.1, HTTP/2, and HTTP/3 on the **same port**.\n"
"Clients discover HTTP/3 availability through the `Alt-Svc` response header on HTTP/1.1 and HTTP/2 responses, then upgrade to QUIC/UDP for subsequent requests."
msgstr "Quarkus 在 *同一端口上* 同时支持 HTTP/1.1、HTTP/2 和 HTTP/3。客户端通过 HTTP/1.1 和 HTTP/2 响应中的 `Alt-Svc` 响应头检测 HTTP/3 的可用性，随后在后续请求中升级至 QUIC/UDP。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Getting started"
msgstr "入门指南"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Add the `quarkus-http3` extension to your project:"
msgstr "将 `quarkus-http3` 扩展添加到您的项目中："

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "pom.xml"
msgstr "pom.xml"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "build.gradle"
msgstr "build.gradle"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"HTTP/3 requires TLS.\n"
"In **dev and test mode**, a TLS certificate is auto-generated if none is configured (see <<auto-tls>>).\n"
"In **production**, you must configure TLS explicitly — see the xref:tls-registry-reference.adoc[TLS registry reference] for details."
msgstr "HTTP/3 需要 TLS。在 *开发和测试模式下* ，如果未配置 TLS 证书，系统会自动生成一个（参见 <<auto-tls>> ）。 *在生产环境中* ，必须显式配置 TLS —— 详情请参阅 xref:tls-registry-reference.adoc[TLS 注册表参考文档] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"With TLS in place, HTTP/3 is enabled automatically.\n"
"No additional configuration is needed."
msgstr "启用 TLS 后，HTTP/3 会自动启用。无需进行额外配置。"

