msgstr "运行 `quarkus tls generate-quarkus-ca --install` 命令，以创建开发证书颁发机构（Dev CA）并将其安装到系统的受信任存储中，从而获得最佳的开发体验。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"When auto-TLS is active, plain HTTP requests are **redirected to HTTPS** by default.\n"
"To allow plain HTTP alongside HTTPS, set:"
msgstr "当自动 TLS 功能处于启用状态时，明文 HTTP 请求默认会被 *重定向到 HTTPS* 。若要允许明文 HTTP 与 HTTPS 并存，请设置："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
