#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Quarkus HTTP server listens on the HTTPS port (default `8443`) for both TCP (HTTP/1.1, HTTP/2) and UDP (HTTP/3 over QUIC) traffic.\n"
"There is no separate port for HTTP/3."
msgstr "Quarkus HTTP 服务器在 HTTPS 端口（默认 `8443` ）上监听 TCP（HTTP/1.1、HTTP/2）和 UDP（基于 QUIC 的 HTTP/3）流量。HTTP/3 没有单独的端口。"

