msgstr "这会告知客户端，同一端口上支持 HTTP/3。支持 HTTP/3 的浏览器和 HTTP 客户端将在后续请求中切换到 QUIC。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "To disable the `Alt-Svc` header:"
