#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Transparent to application code"
msgstr "对应用程序代码而言是透明的"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/http3-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"HTTP/3 does not change how you write application code.\n"
"The same Jakarta REST resources, Vert.x routes, filters, and interceptors work across all HTTP versions.\n"
"You can check the protocol version of a request using `HttpServerRequest.version()` if needed."
msgstr "HTTP/3 不会改变您编写应用程序代码的方式。相同的 Jakarta REST 资源、Vert.x 路由、过滤器和拦截器在所有 HTTP 版本中均可正常工作。如有需要，您可以使用 `HttpServerRequest.version()` 方法检查请求的协议版本。"

